This is a crypto web app created using streamlit. 
It pulls API data on the top 100 cryptos from coinmarketcap.com
Displays key data as a dataframe, shows a bar chart of percent change
Allows user the following options: 
--select which currency to denominate prices in *USD *BTC or *ETH
-- Choose which of the top 100 cryptos to display
-- Use a slider to limit the # of cryptos from 0 ->100
-- Select the time frame for which to measure %change in price (1 hour, 24 hours, 1 week )

Credit to 'the Data Professor' for the streamlit layout. 
